parameters.description: The code to run. Can be a file ID from within Oneflow.
parameters.name: code
parameters.value:
import re
text = r"""$retrieve_original_message.body.value.#.body"""
urls = []
domains = []
url_pattern = r"(http?://\S+)"
for match in re.findall(url_pattern, text):
  clean_match = match.replace("\\", "")
  urls.append(clean_match)
  domain = re.findall(r"^http?://([^/]+)", clean_match)[0]
  domains.append(domain)
print(urls)
